&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Monthly incentives&lt;/strong&gt; based on sales volume for the first 36 months&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Quarterly production bonuses&lt;/strong&gt; for the first 36 months&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Leverage established books of business&lt;/strong&gt; while learning the business&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Access to a &lt;strong&gt;niche market&lt;/strong&gt; that increases your potential for success&lt;/li&gt;
